sequenceDiagram
    actor Recipient
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant API as tRPC API
    participant Encrypt as Encryption Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Audit as Audit Logger

    Recipient->>UI: Open share link
    UI->>API: secrets.accessShare token
    API->>DB: SELECT SecretShare
    DB-->>API: share row
    API->>API: validate token, expiration, views
    alt Token invalid or expired
        API-->>UI: error
        UI-->>Recipient: Link invalid or expired
    else Valid
        alt Password protected
            API-->>UI: prompt password
            Recipient->>UI: enter password
            UI->>API: password
        end
        API->>DB: SELECT Secret
        DB-->>API: encrypted secret
        API->>Encrypt: decrypt
        Encrypt-->>API: plaintext
        API->>DB: increment view count
        API->>Audit: log view event
        API-->>UI: secret content
        UI-->>Recipient: Display secret
    end
